<!-- CONTEXT -->
<h2>Contextul Proiectului</h2>
<p>O platformƒÉ SaaS de colaborare stabilƒÉ de 3 ani cu 800 clien»õi activi »ôi 250.000 EUR ARR se confruntƒÉ cu problema stagnƒÉrii veniturilor. Modelul de pricing era elementar »ôi nedifen»õiat: un singur nivel de 99 EUR/lunƒÉ pentru to»õi clien»õii, indiferent de mƒÉrime sau use case. Problema acesta limiteazƒÉ scalabilitatea »ôi lasƒÉ bani pe masƒÉ din segmentele premium »ôi enterprise.</p>

<!-- DEEP DIVE CHALLENGES -->
<h2>ProvocƒÉri Strategice Profunde</h2>

<div class="challenges-grid">
  <div class="challenge-card">
    <div class="challenge-icon">üí∞</div>
    <div class="challenge-title">Model de Pricing Elementar »ôi Nedifen»õiat</div>
    <div class="challenge-text">Un singur tier la 99 EUR/lunƒÉ trateazƒÉ to»õi clien»õii la fel, indiferent de valoare. SMB-urile »ôi enterprise-urile plƒÉtesc acela»ôi pre»õ, care nu reflectƒÉ diferen»õa de valoare. Rezultat: pierdere de revenue »ôi friction la v√¢nzƒÉri.</div>
    <div class="challenge-impact">Impact: ~40% din enterprise prospects refuzƒÉ sƒÉ cumpere din cauza pricing-ului generic</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="challenge-card">
    <div class="challenge-icon">üìâ</div>
    <div class="challenge-title">Stagnare de Revenue »ôi ProblemƒÉ de Scalabilitate</div>
    <div class="challenge-text">ARR pe ultimii 12 luni: crescut de la 0 la 250K (bun), dar apoi s-a plafonat. De»ôi clien»õii cresc, veniturile nu cresc cu aceea»ôi vitezƒÉ. Problema: nu avem mecanismƒÉ de upsell sau premium offerings.</div>
    <div class="challenge-impact">Impact: Orice cre»ôtere de clien»õi = cre»ôtere liniarƒÉ revenue, nu exponen»õialƒÉ</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="challenge-card">
    <div class="challenge-icon">üìä</div>
    <div class="challenge-title">LTV/CAC Ratio SlabƒÉ »ôi Unit Economics Problematice</div>
    <div class="challenge-text">LTV/CAC = 3.2x (target: 3x+), dar e calculatƒÉ pe un singur year. Pe multi-year, situa»õia se deterioreazƒÉ. Churn de ~8%/an reduce LTV substan»õial. Necesar: cre»ôtere ARPU »ôi reducere churn.</div>
    <div class="challenge-impact">Impact: Business nu e suficient de rentabil, nici SaaS metrics nu sunt sƒÉnƒÉtoase pentru scaling</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="challenge-card">
    <div class="challenge-icon">üéØ</div>
    <div class="challenge-title">Neclaritate pe Segmentare »ôi Packaging Optim</div>
    <div class="challenge-text">Nu e clar care sunt segmentele profitabile (SMB vs Mid vs Enterprise). Care feature value justificƒÉ un tier mai scump? Cum packaghem features ca sƒÉ maximizez perceived value la fiecare segment?</div>
    <div class="challenge-impact">Impact: Orice strategie de pricing fƒÉrƒÉ segmentare e guess work, nu science</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- METHODOLOGY -->
<section class="methodology-section">
  <h2 style="color: #1a1a1a; border-bottom-color: #1a1a1a; margin-top: 0;">Metodologie: 4 Piloni de Pricing Strategy</h2>
  
  <div class="methodology-grid">
    <div class="method-card">
      <div class="method-number">1</div>
      <div class="method-title">Pricing Audit & Customer Segmentation</div>
      <div class="method-text">Am analiza 800 clien»õi: dimensiune, use case, willingness to pay, churn patterns. Am identificat 3 segmente claire: Growth (500+ clien»õi, $150-500/yr), Professional (250 clien»õi, $1500-3000/yr), Enterprise (50 clien»õi, $5000-15000/yr).</div>
      <div class="method-tools">Tools: SQL queries, Python analysis, survey tools, Typeform</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="method-card">
      <div class="method-number">2</div>
      <div class="method-title">Value-Based Pricing Model Design</div>
      <div class="method-text">Am construit 3 tiers cu feature differentiation: Growth ($99/mo, basic features), Professional ($349/mo, advanced features), Enterprise ($999+/mo, custom). Fiecare tier designed pe baza value perception »ôi willingness to pay.</div>
      <div class="method-tools">Tools: Van Westendorp price sensitivity analysis, Feature bundling, Buyer persona research</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="method-card">
      <div class="method-number">3</div>
      <div class="method-title">Migration Strategy & Customer Mapping</div>
      <div class="method-text">Am creat playbook pentru migrare gradualƒÉ: existing clien»õi rƒÉm√¢n la old pricing, new clien»õi pe new pricing. Enterprise prospects primesc custom quotes. Objective: minimize churn pe migration, maximize adoption pe new tiers.</div>
      <div class="method-tools">Tools: Migration spreadsheet, CRM automation, Email campaigns</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="method-card">
      <div class="method-number">4</div>
      <div class="method-title">A/B Testing & Optimization Continuous</div>
      <div class="method-text">Am rulat A/B tests pe landing page pricing, checkout flow, email copy. Am tested 5 varia»õii de tiers (2, 3, 4 tiers). Am monirizat conversion rate, churn, ARPU weekly. Iterate based pe data.</div>
      <div class="method-tools">Tools: Optimizely A/B testing, Google Analytics, Mixpanel analytics, Stripe webhook events</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

